<br />

<br />
THis is just for comparison. And Yes it is a two hander but the shadow night epic 1.5 has Damage: 61 Delay: 35 has almost double the damage to delay while the 2.0 has almost triple. mostly everything was improved on from the 1.5 some stats did remain the same. So we should see something in the line of tha warrior epic. 
<br />

<br />
So what do you think they will give bards. Now keep in mind the procs and focus effect are similar on both the 1.5 and the 2.0 also there are only two classes epic 2.0 found so far and thats warrior and shadownight. 
<br />

<br />
The main reason I am posting this is that besides damage what else can they do to the bard epic to make it better than 1.5? Add Regen? health/manna. Better stats? (maybe a bit but anymore and it would unballance bards over other classes) 
<br />

<br />
Of course instrument mods have got to go up, This is my only prediction. i'd say probaly to 160% instead of 120% maybe more. Maybe less.  
<br />

<br />
Remeber out instrument mods are our focus effect so don't complain about everyone else having a fucus effect.
<br />

<br />
Then again we haven't seen other classes 2.0's yet. I'd like to see all of them just for comparison. The warior epic is a 1hs and is only 28 damage to 26 delay on the 1.5 but jumps to 46 damage 29 delay. But we are not warriors.
<br />

<br />
Rao</span></td>
